Sleek icon pack but the clock widget stops updating time after a while. Only way to refresh it is to remove it and then re-add. Any suggestions? Edit: turned off battery optimization and it still stopped updating. Actually seems like it froze specifically when I plugged the phone in to charge.
replyContent: Hi, if the widget isn't updating, you may need to disable battery optimization for the lines app in your system settings.
